Build Strength.goal: For my long-term health building and maintaining muscle mass is the most important fitness goal, but I don't want to neglect cardio. In general I like to be challenged with mostly medium to hard workouts. Every now and then I need a day to rest and do an easy workout for recovery. I do not like barre or pilates for strength workouts. Even if these workouts are suggested they should be ignored.

Run 5K.goal: I want to go from couch to 5k in the next month.
